item.title: CVE-2019-0322|2024-08-04T17:44:16.479Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20commerce%20cloud%20%28ex%20sap%20hybris%20commerce%29%20%28hy_com%29
item.description: SAP Commerce Cloud (previously known as SAP Hybris Commerce), (HY_COM, versions 6.3, 6.4, 6.5, 6.6, 6.7, 1808, 1811), allows an attacker to prevent legitimate users from accessing a service, either by crashing or flooding the service.
